53 2. (1) Notwithstanding the provisions of section
54 163.011 to the contrary, beginning in school year 2026-27
55 and for each subsequent school year, the state aid
56 calculation for the school districts delineated in
57 subdivision (4) of this subsection shall be calculated using
58 the definition of "local effort" contained in subsection 4
59 of this section and not the definition of "local effort"
60 provided in section 163.011.
