62 to the contrary, beginning in school year 2026-27 and for
63 each subsequent school year, no school district delineated
64 in subdivision (4) of this subsection shall receive any
65 funds under section 163.044.
66 (3) Notwithstanding the provisions of section 163.031
67 to the contrary, beginning in school year 2026-27 and for
68 each subsequent school year, no school district delineated
69 in subdivision (4) of this subsection shall receive state
70 aid calculated under subsection 2 of section 163.031.
71 (4) Subdivisions (1) to (3) of this subsection apply
72 to the following school districts:
73 (a) A school district whose boundaries wholly contain
74 a city with more than two hundred sixty but fewer than two
75 hundred ninety-three inhabitants and located in a county
76 with more than fifteen thousand seven hundred but fewer than
77 seventeen thousand six hundred inhabitants and with a county
