113 (3) Subdivisions (1) and (2) of this subsection apply
114 to the following school districts:
115 (a) A school district whose boundaries wholly contain
116 a city with more than one thousand five hundred but fewer
117 than one thousand seven hundred inhabitants and located in a
118 county with more than seven thousand but fewer than eight
119 thousand inhabitants and with a county seat with fewer than
120 four hundred eighty inhabitants;
121 (b) A school district whose boundaries wholly contain
122 a city with more than seven thousand but fewer than eight
123 thousand inhabitants and that is the county seat of a county
124 with more than fifteen thousand seven hundred but fewer than
125 seventeen thousand six hundred inhabitants;
126 (c) A school district whose boundaries wholly contain
127 a city with more than two thousand seven hundred but fewer
128 than three thousand inhabitants and located in a county with
